{"title":"春暖花开","authors":["郭小川"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":1,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春暖花开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭小川"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国布满生机。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北方飘雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦根儿在雪下伸腰肢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南国花开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布谷鸟在花间啼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东海扬波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白浪映得岸上绿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西部飞砂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风砂滚滚舞新枝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惹得世界欢欢喜喜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处有春意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小虫睡醒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸伸懒腰展开翅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雁儿高啭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤来采云游天际。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳条招手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为田野招徕行旅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风儿漫舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暗将情思传递。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使天下皆诗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万物扬眉吐气。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水解冻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吵吵嚷嚷奔向水库去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小草发芽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硬着头皮顶破地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地喷香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逗引铁牛儿来下犁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山抬头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴望主人插红旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真是斗争节日！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁是春天主人？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快把春天占据。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春在人心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毋须广播消息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春遍人间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用邮电通知。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人在哪里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春在哪里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何必远去寻觅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人心有多高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天有多好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春从人意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好朋友呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好同志！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到春天来吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫迟疑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春暖花开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是英雄用武之时。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大好江山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是呼风唤雨之地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"懒汉哲学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要丢弃！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士胸襟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不容一丝儿娇气！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好姊妹呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好兄弟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到春天来吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫游移！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里长征，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仅仅是个开始，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前途正远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还不是休闲时日。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"困难重重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岂能吓住英雄儿女！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千辛万苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们又何所畏惧？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好朋友呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好同志！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到春天来吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫沉迷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是一张白纸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无尽宝藏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还关在深深地底。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进步伐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岂能半路停止？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能工巧匠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还不施展高超技艺？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好姊妹呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好兄弟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到春天来吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫粗心大意！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正对着我们咬牙切齿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能不警惕？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堂堂中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"理应天下无敌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设事业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必须一天比一天壮丽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们不会辜负春天美景。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这片国土上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住满英雄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年像赵云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老年赛黄忠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿童似哪吒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少年像罗成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"婆婆好似佘太君，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女如同穆桂英。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好传统，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万古长青。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人心上春意浓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这片国土上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"财富无穷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子勇敢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老战士忠诚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女性多美德，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮年精力旺盛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子欢笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘多情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俊美外表，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏着俊美心灵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当春到人间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花舞春城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们满载着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满腹文章，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满腔歌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早晨寒流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"傍晚黄风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在高高天上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放出意志如虹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在广阔大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"散发着热气腾腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当春色满园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水解冻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们满怀着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗决心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进激情；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑迎着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拂晓云霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄昏亮星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在田野里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追逐那青春踪影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在山岗上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举手掀动天空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1958年飞去了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看不见迹踪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它那彩笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却已把我们的心儿染红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘不了："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那蓬勃气象，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动人场景。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想不尽："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那英雄故事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"优美歌声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好时光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么不停一停？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1959年飞来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身子一样儿轻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的脚步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已把我们唤醒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那白色晨光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色前程；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禁不住："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手舞足蹈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心高气盛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好年头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再创造个好年成！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的儿女呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸襟开阔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心地光明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说得到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"办得到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"言必顾行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事务多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"责任重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们甘愿担承。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半点虚夸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半点浮躁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让它一起化作清风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的儿女呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有志气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有本领。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千山万水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骤雨狂风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早不陌生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腿儿酸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筋骨痛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌不过心肠硬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半分骄气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半分懒惰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决不让它度过寒冬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友、同志呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们多么好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们的决心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比天还高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快迈开虎步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺起熊腰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向田野，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向山坳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向大地索取财富，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向高山索取珍宝！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正为我们鸣锣开道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一万零五百亿斤粮食，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是铁的指标；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一亿担棉花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半担也不可少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年大计，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在今朝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春到人间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快和春天赛跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿出壮志雄心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把田间大闹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让一切困难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们面前双膝跪倒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兄弟、姊妹呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们真是一代天骄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们的干劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲九霄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快举起铁锤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿起钻镐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向炉边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进坑道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放出钢水如江河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打开大自然奥妙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春光明媚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在我们头上照耀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一千八百万吨钢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定要牢靠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三亿八千万吨煤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必须达到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰功伟绩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁创造？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英勇斗士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不辞劳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"层层关口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难挡道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛苦吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不值一笑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，春天来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的主人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不负春光好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛勤劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢斗争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天才为我们报效。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春色新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人儿振奋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人心与春色齐飘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春有精神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人也雀跃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，春天来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的主人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把春天打扮得更美妙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗漫卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人群鼎沸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天才如此多娇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春在人里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人在春里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人和春天融在一道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人儿年青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春也不老。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人间幸福知多少！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知心的人儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫错怪我轻佻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是一为今日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二为明朝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万山丛中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种仙桃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大戈壁里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"探油苗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一生辛苦一生乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮丽的前程难画描！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人间喜气万丈高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知心的人儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫错怪我浮飘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不是仅为个人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不是仅为家小。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一腔热血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似火烧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满付精力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如刀出鞘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓为共产主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打开阳关大道！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}